---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout title="SCP 培训认证 | Synapse Certified Practitioner">
  <section class="max-w-4xl mx-auto px-6 py-20">
    <p class="text-sm font-semibold tracking-widest text-[#FCAD2A] uppercase mb-4">TRAINING</p>
    <h1 class="text-4xl font-extrabold text-[var(--color-text)] mb-4">Synapse Certified Practitioner</h1>
    <p class="text-[var(--color-text-light)] text-lg mb-6">学会用 Harness Engineering 构建你自己的 AI Agent 协作运营体系。</p>

    <!-- Lab preview -->
    <div class="mb-12 rounded-xl overflow-hidden border border-[var(--color-border)] shadow-md">
      <div class="bg-[#f0f0f0] px-4 py-2 flex items-center gap-2 border-b border-[#e0e0e0]">
        <div class="flex gap-1.5"><div class="w-2.5 h-2.5 rounded-full bg-[#ff5f57]"></div><div class="w-2.5 h-2.5 rounded-full bg-[#febc2e]"></div><div class="w-2.5 h-2.5 rounded-full bg-[#28c840]"></div></div>
        <div class="flex-1 mx-3"><div class="bg-white rounded px-3 py-0.5 text-[10px] text-[#999] text-center">SCP Lab — Hands-on Workshop</div></div>
      </div>
      <div class="bg-[#0A1628] p-5 text-xs font-mono text-white/60 leading-relaxed">
        <p class="text-[#FCAD2A] mb-2"># Lab 2: Create Your AI Team</p>
        <p class="text-white/40 mb-2">Build organization.yaml + 3 agent profiles</p>
        <p>specialists:</p>
        <p>  - strategist      <span class="text-[#28c840]"># Score: 96/100 ✓</span></p>
        <p>  - tech_lead        <span class="text-[#28c840]"># Score: 92/100 ✓</span></p>
        <p>  - qa_engineer      <span class="text-[#28c840]"># Score: 91/100 ✓</span></p>
        <p class="mt-2 text-[#028CDC]">audit_all_agents() → Average: 93.0/100 · PASS ✓</p>
        <p class="text-[#FCAD2A] mt-1">🎓 SCP Certification: ELIGIBLE</p>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="bg-[#F7F8FA] border border-[var(--color-border)] rounded-xl p-8 mb-8">
      <div class="grid md:grid-cols-4 gap-6 text-center">
        <div><div class="text-2xl font-bold text-[#013A7D]">8 小时</div><div class="text-sm text-[var(--color-muted)]">课程时长</div></div>
        <div><div class="text-2xl font-bold text-[#013A7D]">4 + 4</div><div class="text-sm text-[var(--color-muted)]">理论 + 实操</div></div>
        <div><div class="text-2xl font-bold text-[#FCAD2A]">4 Labs</div><div class="text-sm text-[var(--color-muted)]">动手工作坊</div></div>
        <div><div class="text-2xl font-bold text-[#028CDC]">SCP</div><div class="text-sm text-[var(--color-muted)]">认证证书</div></div>
      </div>
    </div>

    <h2 class="text-xl font-bold text-[var(--color-text)] mb-6">课程内容</h2>
    <div class="space-y-3 mb-12">
      <div class="flex gap-4 items-start p-4 bg-white border border-[var(--color-border)] rounded-lg hover:shadow-sm transition-shadow">
        <span class="text-[#FCAD2A] font-black text-lg shrink-0">M1</span>
        <div><div class="font-semibold text-[var(--color-text)]">为什么需要 Harness Engineering</div><div class="text-sm text-[var(--color-muted)]">真实案例 — 写了规则但没人遵守的教训</div></div>
      </div>
      <div class="flex gap-4 items-start p-4 bg-white border border-[var(--color-border)] rounded-lg hover:shadow-sm transition-shadow">
        <span class="text-[#FCAD2A] font-black text-lg shrink-0">M2</span>
        <div><div class="font-semibold text-[var(--color-text)]">Guides + Sensors 双保险机制</div><div class="text-sm text-[var(--color-muted)]">前馈控制 + 反馈控制的协作设计</div></div>
      </div>
      <div class="flex gap-4 items-start p-4 bg-white border border-[var(--color-border)] rounded-lg hover:shadow-sm transition-shadow">
        <span class="text-[#FCAD2A] font-black text-lg shrink-0">M3</span>
        <div><div class="font-semibold text-[var(--color-text)]">四级决策体系设计</div><div class="text-sm text-[var(--color-muted)]">为什么专家先于CEO — L1自动→L2专家→L3管理→L4高管</div></div>
      </div>
      <div class="flex gap-4 items-start p-4 bg-white border border-[var(--color-border)] rounded-lg hover:shadow-sm transition-shadow">
        <span class="text-[#FCAD2A] font-black text-lg shrink-0">M4</span>
        <div><div class="font-semibold text-[var(--color-text)]">Agent HR 管理体系</div><div class="text-sm text-[var(--color-muted)]">能力分级(A/B/C)、入职审批、自动审计引擎</div></div>
      </div>
      <div class="flex gap-4 items-start p-4 bg-white border border-[var(--color-border)] rounded-lg hover:shadow-sm transition-shadow">
        <span class="text-[#FCAD2A] font-black text-lg shrink-0">M5</span>
        <div><div class="font-semibold text-[var(--color-text)]">情报闭环与自动化编排</div><div class="text-sm text-[var(--color-muted)]">每日情报管线、4专家评审制、自动化事件链</div></div>
      </div>
    </div>

    <h2 class="text-xl font-bold text-[var(--color-text)] mb-6">实操工作坊</h2>
    <div class="grid md:grid-cols-2 gap-4 mb-12">
      <div class="p-5 bg-white border border-[var(--color-border)] rounded-lg"><span class="text-[#028CDC] font-bold text-sm">Lab 1</span><h3 class="font-semibold text-[var(--color-text)] mt-1">搭建你的 Harness Configuration</h3><p class="text-sm text-[var(--color-muted)] mt-1">编写 CLAUDE.md — 角色/执行链/决策/检查点</p></div>
      <div class="p-5 bg-white border border-[var(--color-border)] rounded-lg"><span class="text-[#028CDC] font-bold text-sm">Lab 2</span><h3 class="font-semibold text-[var(--color-text)] mt-1">创建你的 AI 团队</h3><p class="text-sm text-[var(--color-muted)] mt-1">组织架构 + Agent 卡片（审计≥90分）</p></div>
      <div class="p-5 bg-white border border-[var(--color-border)] rounded-lg"><span class="text-[#028CDC] font-bold text-sm">Lab 3</span><h3 class="font-semibold text-[var(--color-text)] mt-1">构建情报管线</h3><p class="text-sm text-[var(--color-muted)] mt-1">行业搜索范围 + 首期报告生成</p></div>
      <div class="p-5 bg-white border border-[var(--color-border)] rounded-lg"><span class="text-[#028CDC] font-bold text-sm">Lab 4</span><h3 class="font-semibold text-[var(--color-text)] mt-1">综合演练 + 答辩</h3><p class="text-sm text-[var(--color-muted)] mt-1">展示体系 + 评审 + SCP 认证</p></div>
    </div>

    <h2 class="text-xl font-bold text-[var(--color-text)] mb-6">定价</h2>
    <div class="grid md:grid-cols-3 gap-4 mb-12">
      <div class="p-6 bg-white border border-[var(--color-border)] rounded-xl text-center">
        <p class="text-sm text-[var(--color-muted)]">个人</p>
        <p class="text-3xl font-bold text-[var(--color-text)] mt-2">$500</p>
        <p class="text-sm text-[var(--color-muted)] mt-2">线上课程 + 实操 + SCP认证</p>
      </div>
      <div class="p-6 bg-white border-2 border-[#FCAD2A] rounded-xl text-center shadow-lg">
        <p class="text-sm text-[#FCAD2A] font-semibold">企业（20人内）</p>
        <p class="text-3xl font-bold text-[#FCAD2A] mt-2">$10K</p>
        <p class="text-sm text-[var(--color-muted)] mt-2">定制内容 + 现场Workshop</p>
      </div>
      <div class="p-6 bg-white border border-[var(--color-border)] rounded-xl text-center">
        <p class="text-sm text-[var(--color-muted)]">企业（50人内）</p>
        <p class="text-3xl font-bold text-[var(--color-text)] mt-2">$15K</p>
        <p class="text-sm text-[var(--color-muted)] mt-2">含1个月后续咨询支持</p>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="text-center">
      <a href="mailto:lysanderl@janusd.io?subject=SCP%20培训咨询" class="inline-block px-10 py-4 bg-[#FCAD2A] text-[#0A1628] rounded-lg font-bold hover:opacity-90 transition-opacity">咨询培训</a>
    </div>
  </section>
</Layout>
